3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves the use of deep learning models for animal identification. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper involves the construction of a database of red panda images for evaluation purposes. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper involves the use of images for animal identification.
